-- Siemens in Talks to Sell Its 35% Voith Hydro Stake, Sueddeutsche Reports
-- Richard Weiss
-- 2010-07-12T06:52:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/siemens-in-talks-to-sell-its-35-voith-hydro-stake-sueddeutsche-reports.html

          
          
             Siemens AG is negotiating to sell
its 35 percent stake in Voith Hydro Holding GmbH & Co., a hydro-
electric power plant maker, to Voith AG,  Sueddeutsche Zeitung 
reported, citing people familiar with the matter.  
 Siemens plans to focus on solar power, tidal power
technology and wind energy; it and Voith have agreed on the
transaction in principle and are talking about the selling
price, the newspaper said.  
